992年血癌病逝。<br />\n<br />\n1985年，屯門景峰兩房單位才賣17萬，50萬即係三層樓。今日若有人拎三層樓收買議員改班馬線，有幾多人會拒絕？<br />\n<br />\n為一條班馬線就劈人，狂劈當年新西以至全港最好的議員<br />\n<br />\n這就是鄉事派，這就是劉皇發。</blockquote>"},{"pid":"e32e08af28d6d6f36bbaa730901d2e1fc5bcabd5","tid":333442,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T05:17:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>請正皮前post</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n討論喺呢度，前post仍可撳正皮<br />\n向10000進發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n前post：<br />\n鄉議局前主席劉皇發逝世　享年80歲<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/332510/page/1?ref=web\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/332510/page/1?ref=web</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n不過，死後報應有鬼用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3bd2d744e45445497a66a58ea7ecc7c5dbab4c3","tid":333442,"uid":65818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T06:37:54.000Z","msg":"抵死"},{"pid":"ce6442bd6b3ad6b5c96cb5d77114d1e8c95ea0b7","tid":333442,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T06:40:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b625d148a05f10b39223f6cc16cdc7fba7ace948","tid":333442,"uid":49316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T06:42:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>代樓主貼返：<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/conradwu/posts/10155644387750774\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fconradwu%2Fposts%2F10155644387750774&d=ojNS2Ttr%2FPNUVTMwEFwojI9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=a70872b3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/conradwu/posts/10155644387750774</a><br />\n<br />\n【說個舊屯門人都知的故事】<br />\n<br />\n八十年代，劉皇發旗下的屯門鄉事想在新墟自己酒樓門口，強行更改班馬線安排於是拿著50萬，想收買吳明欽 (差吳明欽一票就通過)。你估自小窮困嘅吳明欽先生怎回答?<br />\n<br />\n「你畀五億都買唔到我！」<br />\n<br />\n幾日後，議案不能通過，吳明欽就被人用水喉鐵圍劈，身體越來越差。1992年血癌病逝。<br />\n<br />\n1985年，屯門景峰兩房單位才賣17萬，50萬即係三層樓。今日若有人拎三層樓收買議員改班馬線，有幾多人會拒絕？<br />\n<br />\n為一條班馬線就劈人，狂劈當年新西以至全港最好的議員<br />\n<br />\n這就是鄉事派，這就是劉皇發。</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n祝佢落去地獄同老毛一齊俾牛頭馬面屌屎忽"},{"pid":"3f4a25954555d1d1e93b4979a655a96e57fd5131","tid":333442,"uid":84081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T06:55:04.000Z","msg":"癌症折磨得年幾兩年真係益左佢<br />\n<br />\n口德-10分"},{"pid":"037cfaebcab500fca38a322f75f3f63ebddaeb41","tid":333442,"uid":84081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T07:00:58.000Z","msg":"劉皇叔既酒樓係邊間? <br />\n唔想俾帛金"},{"pid":"6c599cedc0fc128adb5806e79c61d7d9f802de5d","tid":333442,"uid":90702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T07:04:23.000Z","msg":"發叔係地獄俾負皮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}